  <h2>5. Subscription and Payment</h2>

  <h3>5.1 Atlassian Marketplace billing</h3>
  <p>OrgPulse subscriptions are purchased and managed through the Atlassian Marketplace. Billing, invoicing, and payment processing are handled by Atlassian in accordance with Atlassian's Marketplace terms. We do not directly process payment card information.</p>

  <h3>5.2 Subscription plans</h3>
